This is the current working verison of the first Lore Pack as it is in development.

Special thanks to Victor Lapin for advice and review of the work on the first Flashpoint and for answering what must 
have seemed like pretty basic questions.

INSTALLATION

Drag and drop the folder into your BT mods folder. 

CURRENT DEPENDENCIES

- ModTek
- BT_Extended
- BT_Extended_Timeline
- Timeline
- ExtendedConversations
- Mission Control
- ColourfulFlashPoint

FLASHPOINT NOTES

Most of the Lore Pack flashpoints are date dependent and have hard open and close dates. New events are used to draw
your attention to them.

TOURING TIKONOV 
Touring Tikonov is set up as an introductory FP for units created in 3028 as a challenging but not overly hard
introduction to the Fourth Succession War Davion series of Flashpoints that are in development. 
Start Date: 14-04-3028
Close Date: 01-07-3028
